overview: The user initiated a review of a sleep questionnaire application,
  providing a Statement of Work and a detailed questionnaire specification. The
  agent conducted a comprehensive analysis of the existing codebase, identifying
  both well-implemented features and significant gaps. A structured plan was
  then created, prioritizing 8 key areas for enhancement, such as implementing a
  1-10 tiredness severity scale, detecting Comorbid Insomnia and Sleep Apnea
  (COMISA), and integrating outbound educational links. The agent has commenced
  the implementation phase, starting with the integration of the tiredness
  severity scale into the application's data types, validation schema, and user
  interface.
